			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">The Secrets of the Sea Hidden High in the Andes</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">The rich fossil deposits in Colombia’s mountains could unlock a deeper understanding of ancient oceans—and the country’s paleontologists are struggling to do them justice.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/santiago-florez/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Santiago Flórez</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						January 23, 2024 | 2,100 words, about 10 minutes					</aside>
