								<img width="900" height="432" src="https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header2-whale-fossil-puzzle.jpg" class="insidepagethumb wp-post-image" alt="North Atlantic right whale displayed at the National Museum of Natural History in Washington, D.C." decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header2-whale-fossil-puzzle.jpg 2500w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header2-whale-fossil-puzzle-520x250.jpg 520w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header2-whale-fossil-puzzle-768x369.jpg 768w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header2-whale-fossil-puzzle-1200x576.jpg 1200w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header2-whale-fossil-puzzle-1536x738.jpg 1536w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header2-whale-fossil-puzzle-2048x984.jpg 2048w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/header2-whale-fossil-puzzle-900x432.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" />								<header class="insidepagethumbinfo">
									<h2>Whales in the Cliff Face</h2>
									<h3>An exposed prehistoric seafloor is a hotspot for ancient whale remains, and now an international team is helping unravel their mysteries.</h3>
									<p class="insidepagethumbinfodate">Feb 15, 2022 | 4,200 words, about 21 minutes</p>
								</header>
								</a>
							</article>
																				<article class="col insidepagethumbholder photo-essays rotator ">
								<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/videos-visuals/salvaging-fossils-on-the-jurassic-coast/" class="tagmanager" id="Related_article_31157" >
